homepage.heroTagline.message: Explore the UnderSilicon Intelligent Ecosystem, Unlock Infinite Interactive Gameplay

支持多种智能终端（电机、跳蛋、脉冲等），极速 WiFi 配网，稳定连接，轻松上手.message: Supports various smart terminals (motors, vibrators, pulse devices, etc.), ultra-fast WiFi configuration, stable connection, easy to get started.

内置俯卧撑检测、电击问答、寸止训练等多种趣味互动模式，让控制更有趣。.message: Built-in push-up detection, electric shock Q&A, edging training, and other fun interactive modes to make control more interesting.

提供强大的电脑客户端与手机端支持（App/小程序），随时随地掌控设备状态。.message: Provides powerful PC client and mobile support (App/Mini Program), allowing you to control device status anytime, anywhere.

提供 Python 控制接口与开源代码，支持开发者自定义扩展，共建智能玩具体验。.message: Provides Python control interfaces and open-source code, supports developer customization and extension, co-creating the smart toy experience.
